-- Gold Fields Meets U.S. Investors on Possible Bond Sale, Business Day Says
-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 2010-09-27T05:24:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-27/gold-fields-meets-u-s-investors-on-possible-bond-sale-business-day-says.html
Gold Fields Ltd. began meeting
fixed-income investors in the U.S. and U.K. to gauge appetite
for another bond issue, Business Day reported, citing Corporate
Affairs Manager Sven Lunsche.  The company started meetings on Sept. 23, according to the
Johannesburg-based newspaper. Repaying or refinancing existing
debt is a priority for the company, Business Day reported
Lunsche as saying.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
